overview:
The Florida Law Offices of Brian Moskowitz helps people with family law issues including divorce, custody, and support.

At the Law Offices of Brian M. Moskowitz, we help South Florida residents with family law legal matters, including adoption, alimony, child support, custody, divorce, domestic violence, guardianship, paternity, visitation, and more.

We understand that a separation and divorce can be among the most stressful experiences in life. Our goal is to guide you through the legal hurdles you’ll face.
